title: Has anyone received their unemployment benefits yet?
text: I had to file for unemployment (I am a receptionist at a dental office) and I still have not received my payments. I am currently on week 3 of unemployment and have bills coming up I will need to pay. Has anyone received their payments yet, and if so did you get your estimated amount plus $600? I was not sure who was eligible for the $600 added amount. Thank you!
